title: coca cola 600  nascar cup series
description: sourced from predicthqcom  the nascar cup series  cocacola 600 is one of the most iconic and longest races in the nascar calendar held annually at the charlotte motor speedway in concord north carolina spanning 600 miles the race tests drivers endurance and skill making it a fanfavorite and a true test of racing prowess traditionally run on memorial day weekend the event also serves as a tribute to the us armed forces adding a patriotic element to the highspeed competition
